TY  - JOUR
T1  - Fractional Programming. II, On Dinkelbach's Algorithm
AU  - Schaible, Siegfried
Y1  - 1976/04/01
PY  - 1976
DA  - 1976/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.22.8.868
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.22.8.868
