TY  - JOUR
T1  - Some Properties of a Decentralized Adjustment Process
AU  - Simonovits, András
Y1  - 1976/04/01
PY  - 1976
DA  - 1976/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.22.8.883
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.22.8.883
